{
  "stem": "1929.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think what they-- the-- the death camps were overrun, so they didn't know what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I swear, they-- Anyhow, at the end of three weeks, we ended up in Theresienstadt, which is in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think they knew where they were taking us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd like to find some history of that, you know, some-- because there must be somebody that has written about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't find it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We ended up in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're coming into Theresienstadt, and we had these Ukrainian guards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were son of a bitches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were the worst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Czech people come out offering us food, and flowers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- and they tell us-- I think they told us that the-- the camp was under Red Cross supervision.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The story goes that, what happened is that, I think, Hitler gave the order to destroy most of the inmates in the camps, so there would be no evidence.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he had orders to destroy Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, Theresienstadt was a beautiful little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the model concentration camp where they brought the Red Cross and other people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was run by the inmates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was little houses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was paradise, for us to get there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And apparently, the commandant of the-- of the Theresienstadt camp, he made a deal with the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when we-- the day that we arrived there, we were-- we were already-- the camp was free.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they would not let us into the main-- the main town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They put us in a compound, because they were-- we were covered with lice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we're covered-- totally covered with lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they-- they quarantined us for, like-- oh, that was the most horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
